; Extended-JSON codec for Bson.t — the bridge to the C driver (libmongoc speaks MongoDB canonical/
; relaxed extended JSON). Emits CANONICAL extended JSON (every typed number wrapped as a string, so
; the codec is precise regardless of the JSON number representation, and Decimal128 is just a
; string libbson interprets) and parses both canonical and relaxed forms back. Pure (Bson + the
; fennec-mongo JSON primitive) — native and browser.
(library
 (name fennec_mongo_bson_json)
 (public_name fennec-mongo.bson_json)
 (libraries fennec-mongo.bson fennec-mongo.json))
